    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "<h2 style=\"margin: 25px 0 10px 0; font-family: 'Figtree', 'Noto Sans', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-style: normal; font-size: 22px; line-height: 30px; color: #0093a4; text-align: center;\">\r\n  Identify, Defend, Reflect!\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"border: 2px solid #4A90E2; padding: 15px; background-color: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\r\n<p><strong>CyberShield Inc. is under attack!</strong></p>\r\n<p>As a cybersecurity analyst, it’s your job to investigate security threats and identify the best defenses to protect the company’s network.</p>\r\n<p>In this <strong>interactive simulation</strong>, you’ll analyze real-world vulnerabilities—like <strong>phishing scams, weak passwords, default credentials, and social engineering tricks</strong>—and decide how to stop them before they cause damage.</p>\r\n<p>Are you ready to <strong>test your cybersecurity skills</strong> and keep CyberShield safe? Let’s get started!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1EVhT6Les4IsI59u1FssuiWn6gtuLIvOerjbMVISxQ5Q/present\r\n\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://images.code.org/46c899ab897999dd45962e5554eaa672-image-1740116339358.png\" width=\"100%\" style=\"border: 3px solid #4A90E2; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n</a>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: center;\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://images.code.org/006d7e43355aae1a8f3a48689f235562-image-1740116300853.png\" width=\"45%\" style=\"margin-right: 10px; border: 3px solid #4A90E2; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n  <img src=\"https://images.code.org/880485acc4ca2cb646cc077783664094-image-1740116387826.png\" width=\"45%\" style=\"border: 3px solid #4A90E2; border-radius: 8px;\">\r\n</div>\r\n",
